				<div class="et_pb_text_inner">For years I was struggling with my digestive health. I had pain when eating bloating, cramps  and I wasn’t absorbing what I was eating. I tried many different alternative health therapies  but none of them gave me lasting results. I was at a point where I felt I couldn’t heal. I  thought it would take years, and that I would never be able to eat wheat or dairy again.<br />
