				<div class="et_pb_text_inner">I came to Matt because I have Hashimoto&#8217;s disease, and I wanted to get my antibodies  down (they were well over 1000, and had been for years). Though Hashis is a thyroid  disease, I believe the root cause, in my case, has stemmed from my gut. In addition to  digestive issues, my biggest symptom was brain fog and fatigue.<br />
